@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ozbncs(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.87)))
    v0 = (0.40 / v0)
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v2 + 0.68)) + tmp)
    v1 = wp.cos(0.32)
    v0 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.99 / v0 + 0.03)) * v2)
    tmp = v1
    tmp = ((0.05 - 0.08) - 0.76)
    v0 = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.07 + v2 + 0.01)) + wp.exp(v1))
    data[tid] = v0
